data.title: Obituary for Pearline W. (Taylor) Mitchell
data.meta_description: Pearline Winola Mitchell, 91, former resident of Wetipquin, Maryland, died Thursday, February 6, 2014 at the Salisbury Genesis Nursing and Rehabilitation Center in Salisbury, MD.Born in Wetipquin, she was the daughter of the late Edward J. and Victoria (Bailey) Taylor.  Her...
